The paper deals with discriminatory channel estimation in MIMO wireless systems, which involves signal processing, communication theory, and network security. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
